cast.overview: Plagued by a violent recurring nightmare, college student Stefanie heads home to track down the one person who might be able to break the cycle and save her family from the grisly demise that inevitably awaits them all.
cast.title: Final Destination Bloodlines

details.biography: Kaitlyn Santa Juana (born April 19, 1997) is a Canadian actress and singer. Santa Juana has worked on the musical “Dear Evan Hansen,” starting with the company in 2019 in its production in Toronto, Canada, before eventually moving on to the Broadway company. She is also known for her roles in the CW series “The Flash” and the film “Final Destination: Bloodlines.” She's of Spanish and Filipino descent.
details.name: Kaitlyn Santa Juana
